title: Jan de Vries Health and Diet Centre
description: A health food store with huge range of herbal and fruit teas, wholefoods including organic and gluten free. Also a large range of herbal remedies and nutritional supplements. Ethical cosmetics and toiletries including organic and fair trade and offers complementary therapies. Part of a Scottish chain founded in the 1950s by Dutch naturopath Jan de Vries, who passed away early 2015.
